Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.50,0:00:06.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.54,0:00:08.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.52,0:00:13.71,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我有事想拜托柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.51,0:00:19.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}虽然还多少有些难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:20.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你能看一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:55.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:01:58.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:03.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那是什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:04.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你看不出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.11,0:02:06.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是手包啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.53,0:02:08.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你到底打算干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.67,0:02:10.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不是说过要抛手包吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.08,0:02:13.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}刚才还漂亮地抛起了三个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:19.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你不相信我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:20.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我说的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.94,0:02:23.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的很漂亮地抛起了三个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:23.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}晚安…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.85,0:02:24.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}别睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:26.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你快回去睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:28.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我还在放哨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.61,0:02:31.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}主人要给你看拿手绝活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.84,0:02:35.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}做臣子的不是该跪下恭恭敬敬地拜见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.75,0:02:36.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}别胡搅蛮缠了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:38.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好  我命令你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:40.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  等等！ 等等！ 等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:45.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}别在这种时候用主人的命令来压我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.55,0:02:48.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我可不想再立什么多余的誓言了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}疼疼疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:54.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}别咬人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:58.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}还不怪你自己太粗暴了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:03.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:06.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我看着就是了  你快点抛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:08.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你说的话… 总是这么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:10.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:10.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:14.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想看想得不得了  你快点抛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}还是那么一点诚意也没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:18.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.20,0:03:22.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看过我的绝技之后  你的态度也就会变了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.23,0:03:27.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我终于找到窍门了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:30.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哼  学会了之后就是这么简单的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:34.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}现在  我已经是不输给里叶的手包名人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:41.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我终于明白  全心全意去学习一件事物是多么地重要了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:43.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:58.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}刚才那绝对是搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:18.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我没说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:20.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的已经学会了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:24.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}谁也没说你说谎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.39,0:04:26.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我看着呢  你尽管抛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:28.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这次一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:29.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}肩膀放松一些嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.31,0:04:32.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不放松一些的话  名人也做不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:34.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是… 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:40.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:43.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎么样  怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:45.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我抛得不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.34,0:04:51.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}能做到这样已经很了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:53.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}用不着安慰我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:54.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这不是安慰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:58.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}能做成这样  是因为你努力练习了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:01.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不懂得放弃可真是了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:04.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}听不懂你到底是在夸我还是在嘲笑我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:06.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是在夸你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:09.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不管怎么说  你干得很好  神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:11.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我还想做得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:14.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}每天都练习的话肯定会变得很拿手的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:16.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真夸张
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:17.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:22.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你还会再看我抛手包吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:25.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  只要你愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.54,0:05:28.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}趁现在快去睡一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.85,0:05:29.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今天还要走很多路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:30.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:48.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看来必须越过这些群山峻岭才行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:54.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}想逃脱追兵的话  在山林里行进是再好不过的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:57.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我去取些水来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.97,0:06:06.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎么了  神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:14.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:20.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}求你饶了我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:24.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}进不去了… 都说过进不去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:26.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}饶了我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:30.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.67,0:06:34.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}已经吃不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:39.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  这么睡的话会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:54.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  别再睡第二觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:00.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也别睡第三觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:03.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也大人  您太手软了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:16.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}很疼的啊  你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:20.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈大人  您感觉好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:22.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你看我像感觉好的样子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:25.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}叫我起床时就不能再温柔些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:29.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那么下次我就再注意一下力度…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.43,0:07:32.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我是让你别再抽枕头了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:43.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你的耳朵可真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:47.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}跑起来的话不会刮到草木上去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:51.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}耳朵这么长的话  可以听得很远吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:08:00.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可恶  居然敢耍我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:02.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  给我停下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:04.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}给我停下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:06.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂！ 停下停下停下停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:07.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:09.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}给我安静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:14.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你一直在看什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:16.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}前几天在集市上找到的地图
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:17.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}很珍贵的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.67,0:08:21.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这些像虫子一样的东西是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:22.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是河流的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:25.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈  你不认识字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:27.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没有人教我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:29.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}又怎么可能认识呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:31.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}里叶居然也不管你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.89,0:08:33.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我才没有不管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:38.99,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因为神奈大人说过「绝对不想跟里叶学字」…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:41.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那不是要怪里叶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.42,0:08:43.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}该不会忘了歌集那件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:47.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那是为了丰富神奈大人的心灵才…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:50.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}靠你那种教人的方法  心灵怎么会丰富得起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:51.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你们在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:56.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}以前  我曾经教过神奈大人背诵和歌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:09:00.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}学习东西当然要付出一点点心血了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:02.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可是神奈大人却…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.03,0:09:07.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一天要背二百首  还叫什么「一点点心血」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.47,0:09:09.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一共有四千五百首呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:11.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}磨磨蹭蹭怎么行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.33,0:09:15.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我已经五天没睡了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:20.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}还剩下二百首  再忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:23.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你的命还真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.53,0:09:25.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:27.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想这样下去肯定会死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:31.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以把歌集全都扔到炉灶里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:35.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}宝贵的古今六帖一并全都变成早饭的柴火了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:40.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那天的饭  真是充满了风流的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:45.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就是这张嘴在胡说八道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.74,0:09:47.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}快放开… 里叶…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:50.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}连一首和歌也唱不出来的嘴巴  根本就是没用的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:52.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}太没道理了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:54.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我干脆把它缝上算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:56.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你还在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:58.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}快救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:02.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可是  我也怕里叶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:04.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你这没用的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:11.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}对不起  我有些太激动了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.16,0:10:12.96,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:14.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}为什么你要原谅她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你的声音还是很怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:18.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:21.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我到那边去练习抛手包了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:23.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在这里待着心会乱的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:26.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那我也陪你一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.86,0:10:28.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}用不着你陪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:34.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}为什么要打我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.01,0:10:37.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我在乱发脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:44.50,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:03.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是和尚吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:05.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}身上没有伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:07.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看来是累倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:22.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}能说一会话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:27.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:28.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}又要抛手包吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:30.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.53,0:11:34.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你是不是有什么心事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:37.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}心事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:37.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:42.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有什么想说的话不必憋在心里  把它说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.42,0:11:43.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}想说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:48.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那我就说一句好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:50.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.78,0:11:52.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你的头顶上有只毛毛虫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:12:00.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你好像很容易吸引野兽和虫子之类的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:02.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}别那么冷静啊  就不能救救我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:06.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}刚才就一直觉得你很古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.22,0:12:09.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}本来想作为主人关心一下臣子来着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:11.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}结果弄得自己这么没面子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:14.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}抱歉  我说给你听就是了  别走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:18.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不会再拿我开玩笑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:21.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这可是很无聊的事情哦  你真的想听吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.77,0:12:23.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你尽管说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:27.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我没见过自己的父母
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:29.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:32.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}大概  是被扔掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:36.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在路边哭泣的时候  被行脚僧捡到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:39.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}行脚僧就是旅行的和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:43.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所谓的行脚僧听起来似乎很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:47.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}其实也只是无家可归  四处乞讨的人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.52,0:12:52.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我们俩一起周游了各种各样的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:56.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}北方 南方 东方 西方  去过各种各样的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:13:00.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}他是柳也的养育之亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:03.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也算不上是什么养育之亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.64,0:13:08.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}他是个严厉的人  除了诵经之外从不开口说闲话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.38,0:13:11.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就连法名最终也没有告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:16.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在大约五岁时的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:23.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我们在山路上遇到了山贼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:26.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}行脚僧被一刀杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:29.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看到刚才那个和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.94,0:13:31.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想起了这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:36.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}原来柳也也没有母亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.89,0:13:42.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可是  我却只顾追寻自己的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:44.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:46.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这也是我的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:52.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那个行脚僧临死前还在祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:56.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}祝愿杀死自己的人能够往升净土
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.09,0:14:00.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}之后  自己死在了血泊中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:02.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我没有被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:07.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}他们说我不值得弄脏他们的刀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.22,0:14:11.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就这样  我又独自一人站在路边了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:19.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那以后  我一直都是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:22.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}为了活下去  我什么都干过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:25.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}偷走过别人的刀枪  参加过战争
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:27.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也杀过人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:30.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}每天都只想着自己如何才能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:34.26,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}直到最近为止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:35.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}最近…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:36.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}最近发生过什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:41.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这就是所谓的心境转变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.68,0:14:44.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只要有一些契机  人都会改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:49.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那些山贼一定也很后悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:53.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}他们杀了一位德高望重的高僧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.29,0:14:54.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}当然会后悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:58.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}很难说他能不能算得上是德高望重的高僧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:00.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你在怀疑什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.14,0:15:03.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}正是因为听到了行脚僧的祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:07.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}山贼们才没有杀害柳也吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:15.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:19.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那个时候  我或许确实是被行脚僧救了一条命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:23.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}为什么没有早点注意到这一点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:26.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那样的话  我就一定会走上另一条道路了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:27.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:31.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那样的话  我不是就遇不到柳也了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.71,0:15:32.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:35.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我也庆幸自己能遇到神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:39.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.68,0:15:43.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.97,0:15:46.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:48.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:48.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:52.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我不知道接下来该怎么做才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:56.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:59.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}后边的事就拜托给柳也了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:11.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我很难为情的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.84,0:16:12.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}快点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:14.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:17.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你真的知道接下来要干什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:20.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}别… 别小看我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:21.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我很清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:23.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}里叶全都教给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.35,0:16:26.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}果然是里叶捣的鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:27.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:30.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也对我来说就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:32.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}虽然说不清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:34.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但是… 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:39.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}里叶说过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:44.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}「柳也说起往事的时候  就别放过那个机会」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:50.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}男性是一定会对喜欢的女性说起往事来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.87,0:16:52.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:54.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}都被她猜中了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:59.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}「听柳也说完后  就慢慢地解开衣服」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:04.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她还说过什么「需要让胸部若隐若现」之类的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.76,0:17:06.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}连导演都做好了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:09.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我弄错什么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:15.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}莫非  柳也只喜欢男色吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:16.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:17.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哦  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:21.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有些男性虽然喜欢女性  却很无能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:23.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}别胡说八道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.72,0:17:26.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}果然还是因为把衣服脱得过头了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:28.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.26,0:17:33.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我就让你知道我也是个男人  你做好准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:36.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也  你的眼神很怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:39.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是你来引诱我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:41.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就老老实实让我用毒牙咬一口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:43.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳… 柳也有毒的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.07,0:17:45.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}男人全都是有毒的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:49.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}而且还有更多你不知道的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:53.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就让我一步一步教你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:56.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  快住手！ 住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:17:58.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:02.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}里叶  你藏在那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:03.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:08.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你依然是那么精明呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:17.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈大人  您没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:20.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不太清楚… 不过似乎不太成功…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:21.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:26.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我惹柳也生气了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:28.71,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我没生气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:33.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}里叶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:36.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你是不是看穿我绝对不会出手的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.19,0:18:39.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}其实我自己也不是很确定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:42.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}天下哪还有我这种人畜无害的男人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:44.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也可以说是无能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.86,0:18:45.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}罗嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:54.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她睡得很香嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.89,0:18:59.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今天也热心地做过手包的修炼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:04.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}睡着的时候  倒是很可爱的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:06.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在无聊男人们聚过来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:09.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}得教会她色恋之事才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:10.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}别用我来练习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.59,0:19:13.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她还是个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.49,0:19:17.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}连人偶和手包都没有玩过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:20.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}母亲大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.15,0:19:23.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}您醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.63,0:19:28.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我做了一个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:31.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是一个在其他地方的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:36.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我穿着奇特的衣装  相貌也改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:39.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那真的是我吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.98,0:19:42.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}变成什么样的相貌了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:44.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}记不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:47.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不过  身边有我的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.05,0:19:50.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}还有很多善良的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:53.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我非常地幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:57.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是个很好的梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:20:00.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只要把这个梦变成现实不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.77,0:20:02.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你马上就能见到母亲了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:06.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那时候  你的梦就不再是梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:07.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.94,0:20:11.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只要虔诚祈祷  上天就一定能够听到我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:25.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看啊  看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.77,0:20:27.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我做得很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:28.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}它们没有掉下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.73,0:20:30.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一个也没有掉下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.65,0:20:50.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看来还需要再修炼一段时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.84,0:20:53.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不过  真的是很棒啊  神奈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.22,0:20:58.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只要继续修炼下去  一定会更加出色的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:20:59.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:03.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}到时候我就可以做给母亲看了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.52,0:21:04.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:17.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我们该走了  神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.55,0:21:22.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎么了  不和我一起来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.05,0:21:35.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那是你的母亲吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:38.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.59,0:21:48.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}要永远幸福地生活下去啊

